{
  "stem": "766.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It is quite far, yeah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By train, I imagine.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah, we both went.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, no, I had nothing to do with them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We ate outside.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Maybe breakfast, I don't remember how it was.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But lunch we ate, there was a mess hall for students, so we ate over there or outside.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I don't remember exact, but nothing to do with the family.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My parents gave me the money, and I paid them, the same that my-- my classmate.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't remember, but maybe.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't think so.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I passed some examination.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I remember, chemistry, I liked very much.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Physics, and botany, and theology, which I did not care too much about.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So this year, what was in the curriculum, I took.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Very little.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, there-- there were, but I didn't date, no.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were plenty of women, yeah.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In Poland were plenty of women.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They knew.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They looked at me, they knew.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The professor, they looked at me, my name was-- and my looks.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, but I want to tell how it was in Krakow.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was a lot of anti-Semitism at the University, because it didn't affect me personally, but it was.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because a few subjects which I took, botany and zoology, were also included in the studying of agriculture, which the young sons of the nobility, the [? landholders, ?] had to take these courses, because others, it wasn't so important.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But they were very nationalistic and probably anti-Semitic, so they were seated on one side, and the Jews were sitting on the left side, separate.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Probably was ordered, but we revolted against this, so we were not sitting, we were standing.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember this, because I was only 17, but I knew.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But there was no beating this, I think.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
